ActPublic Service Superannuation Act
SubjectOrder Amending Schedule I to the Public Service Superannuation Act
PrecisORDER AMENDING SCHEDULE I TO THE PUBLIC SERVICE SUPERANNUATION ACT in order to reflect the dissolution of the National Energy Board (NEB) and the establishment of the Canadian Energy Regulator (CER), thereby supporting the transition of employees of the NEB to the CER.
